cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CE, cs.DB 

This paper is about personalization in eCommerce search, which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR) in computer science. Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, such as latent feature learning and item embeddings, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper deals with ranking and optimization, which are relevant to the sub-categories of computational engineering (cs.CE) and databases (cs.DB).
